---
<section class="product-teaser">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Inaugural Lineup</h2>
    <div class="products-grid">
      <div class="product-card">
        <span class="badge">Coming Soon</span>
        <h3>Jerry Can Dark Rum</h3>
        <p>
          The foundation. Rich, complex, and smooth, built to be savored neat after a long day's journey or as the uncompromising backbone of a classic cocktail. This is where every expedition begins.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="product-card">
        <span class="badge">Coming Soon</span>
        <h3>Expedition Spiced</h3>
        <p>
          A functional spice blend, not a sweet confection. Notes of smoke, peppercorn, and citrus peel. This is the flavor of resourcefulness, designed for the modern explorer who values authenticity over artifice.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .product-teaser {
    /* Use a dark background for contrast */
    background-color: var(--charcoal); 
    padding: 4rem var(--page-padding);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    /* Make the title light to stand out on the dark background */
    color: var(--cream); 
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .products-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); /* A 2-column grid this time */
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .product-card {
    background-color: var(--slate); /* A slightly lighter dark color for the cards */
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 2px solid var(--brass);
    color: var(--cream);
    position: relative; /* Needed for positioning the badge */
    overflow: hidden; /* Keeps the badge's corner effect tidy */
  }

  .product-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--brass); /* Use the brand accent for the product name */
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .product-card p {
    font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -1px;
    right: -1px;
    background-color: var(--brass);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    padding: 8px 16px;
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
  }

  /* Responsive styling for mobile */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .products-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Stack the product cards */
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>